    - Capital Equipment Corporation GPIB cards
    - FMH GPIB HDL core
    - HP 82335
    - HP 82341
    - INES PCI cards
    - LPVO USB GPIB
    - NEC7210
    - NI GPIB-USB-B/HS/HS+
    - TMS9914
    - TNT4882


